snippet.title: The Last Faith - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Last Faith - A dark, gothic alliance of soulslike and metroidvania. Coming 2022 to PC, Switch, PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X|S, and Xbox One.

Wishlist Now: https://bit.ly/3zxDAOU
Talk with us on Discord! https://bit.ly/3QfSSxT

The wicked and the blessed will be judged the same - let nothing stand in your way.
